title: Hongdou Ya
synopsis: The little boy "Animation Bug" and the little girl "Daydream" are smart, active, thinking, fantasizing, confident but a little squeamish. They crossed time and space to the Long March seventy years ago. They met with the Red Army soldiers, especially the "Little The "Red Army" forged pure friendship and experienced many tense, thrilling and even magical stories in the Long March. These short stories are not limited to real people and events at the time, but join the wishes and imaginations of modern children. It does not blindly exaggerate pain and bloodshed, but focuses on the revolutionary ideals and optimism of the Red Army soldiers. The Little Red Army in the film is by no means a simple-minded conceptual character, but the same yearning for happiness and freedom as modern children, as well as various talents and wisdom, the same love of knowledge, yearning for reading, the same pursuit of a happy life, and the same childish flesh and blood and ideal People. title: Yan He Wan
synopsis: The theme of Yanhe Bay is the construction of a new countryside. Take the process of building a new socialist countryside in Yanhewan Village under the guidance of the scientific development concept, and the emotional development of the hero and heroine Shanlin and Caifeng as clues. In the form of paper-cut cartoons, it vividly reflects the interesting people and events that occurred in the construction of the new countryside, and shows the earth-shaking changes that have taken place in the revolutionary sacred place of Yan'an in the 60 years since the founding of the People’s Republic of China, especially since the reform and opening up and the construction of the new countryside. At the same time, it also promoted the party's policy of enriching the people in a brand-new artistic way, showing the unique customs and folk culture of the rural areas of northern Shaanxi. It is a TV show that focuses on the new countryside, new farmers and the spirit of Yan'an in the new era. It is also the only innovative work in the country that reflects the content of the new countryside construction in the form of paper-cut animation.(translated from tenceng)
